WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:01.330
I’m so happy.

00:01.490 --> 00:04.290
Kyoko-chan and Mayu-chan came to visit me at home.

00:04.670 --> 00:05.820
I’m so glad.

00:06.170 --> 00:07.530
I wasn’t disliked.

00:08.030 --> 00:09.820
They were worried about me.

00:10.690 --> 00:13.210
I hope I get over this cold soon so I can go to school.

00:13.880 --> 00:18.660
I want to take Kyoko-chan and Mayu-chan out for a treat because they took notes for me at school.

00:19.280 --> 00:22.250
I wonder if that will make them happy.
